@div proverb 25.10

25.10.28. e₂-gal ud 1(DIŠ)-e# ama!# nir#-ra ud 1(DIŠ)-e ama! u₃-tud-da
#lem: egal[palace]; ud[sun]; n; ama[mother]; nir[lordly]; ud[sun]; n; ama[mother]; utud[give birth (to)]
