#etcsl: line-id=25.11.29

#note: cf. 6.1.02.157, 6.1.14.20, 6.2.3: UET 6/2 317

25.11.30. dumu-gir₁₅ du-lum-ma nu-da₁₃-da₁₃
#lem: dumugir[citizen]; dulum[toil]; taka[set aside]
#etcsl: line-id=25.11.30

@end proverb

@div proverb 25.12

25.12.31. an-ku₄-ku₄ nu-si-si
#lem: kur[enter]; si[fill]
